highlights.text: “Barbaad (From "Saiyaara")” by The Rish and Jubin Nautiyal is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Canada, up 18 spots at #65.
Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Viral Songs Canada. “Tears” is the highest at #11.
“One Last Breath - Remix” by ATLiens has been on Viral Songs Canada the longest, at 100 days straight.
“Her Name Was Fire” by Samuel Cabana is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Canada at #5.
